2
00:01:20,040 --> 00:01:23,080
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:41,320
[Letter of Resignation]

4
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:54,160
Uncle,

5
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:57,280
where are you going so late?

6
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,360
I'm going out for a run.

7
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,000
Why aren't you sleeping yet?

8
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,640
Wait for me.

9
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,600
I'll go with you.

10
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:04,400
No need.

11
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,000
Bao,

12
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:11,000
sorry for worrying you lately.

13
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:13,840
I'm fine.

14
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,480
I'm heading out.

15
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,200
Life is unpredictable.

16
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,600
This is not about regret

17
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,480
but about a turning point.

18
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,240
Only if you believe

19
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,520
can you create possibilities.

20
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:59,040
[Mutton Soup in Shanxian]

21
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,600
Sir,

22
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,680
a bowl of mutton soup, please.

23
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:23,320
Hello.

24
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:24,280
Jiadi.

25
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,600
Come here and help me out.

26
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:27,400
I need you.

27
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,640
What's wrong?

28
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,200
I'll send you the address.

29
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,080
Hurry over.

30
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:41,320
Sir,

31
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,960
cancel the soup.

32
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:46,840
There's no more alcohol.

33
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:49,920
Got it.

34
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,400
You take a rest.

35
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:52,240
I'll go.

36
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:53,240
Everyone,

37
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:54,720
drink to your heart's content.

38
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,120
Alright.

39
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:55,920
Drink to your heart's content.

40
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,240
Tong Xia,

41
00:03:59,040 --> 00:03:59,800
we're out of alcohol.

42
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:00,800
Bring another dozen.

43
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:02,960
I can bring more alcohol,

44
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,480
but no more discounts.

45
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:05,080
You have to pay in full.

46
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:05,960
Come on.

47
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,200
Aren't we friends?

48
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,280
How about this?

49
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,280
We change to...

50
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,960
It's still the original price.

51
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,360
Ma Xiaotiao,

52
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,880
you're crossing the line.

53
00:04:18,960 --> 00:04:20,040
We gave you discounts

54
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:20,640
because of your friend

55
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:21,880
who saved Tong Xia.

56
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,360
But look at you.

57
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,760
The real hero is nowhere to be seen,

58
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:26,560
yet you keep bringing people
to take advantage.

59
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:32,000
The situation changed.

60
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:35,160
My buddy has a girlfriend now.

61
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,480
He can't mess around anymore.

62
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,360
Look.

63
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,960
He's so close to me.

64
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:44,160
Thanking me

65
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:46,040
is as good as thanking him.

66
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,080
Pay in full.

67
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,320
Do you still want it?

68
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,840
You're serious, huh?

69
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,400
Fine.

70
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:55,720
You want to meet Zhao Jiadi, right?

71
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:58,360
Tonight I'll show you

72
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:00,120
what true brotherhood looks like.

73
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,320
Here you go, sir.

74
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,400
Jiadi.

75
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:20,920
What happened?

76
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,920
I knew you wouldn't stand by
and do nothing.

77
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,120
It was really hard to trick you here.

78
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,320
Even offering you business didn't work.

79
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:25,680
Let's go.

80
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:27,360
I'll take you to meet two people.

81
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:29,280
How did meeting the parents go?

82
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:32,560
I don't want to talk about it.

83
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:33,640
It flopped?

84
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:35,720
It's okay. Just find another one.

85
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:38,200
These two people are really important.

86
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,240
[Peach Blossom Books]
Besides your performance,

87
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,760
it's also about my reputation.

88
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,560
Have a few drinks, and change your mood.

89
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:44,760
Jiadi,

90
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,560
this bar is great.

91
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,360
The owner's singing

92
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,640
is top-notch.

93
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:49,720
Dong,

94
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,360
this is my buddy,

95
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,040
Zhao Jiadi.

96
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:52,640
Jiadi.

97
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:53,920
Come on, have a seat.

98
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,920
Come and sit inside.

99
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:56,800
Didn't you meet already?

100
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,640
Hello, Dong.

101
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,840
I finally meet you in person.

102
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,680
Ma bragged about you for so long

103
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,760
that I got sick of it.

104
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:05,160
How could you say that, Dong?

105
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:07,920
I was just expressing my genuine trust

106
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,000
and sincere respect.

107
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:09,960
Come on.

108
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:10,840
Everyone.

109
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,320
Let's drink.

110
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:13,480
Cheers.

111
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,840
Jiadi, I heard

112
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,000
you want

113
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,920
to start a business.

114
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:19,720
Let's talk.

115
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:21,800
I'm still at the drafting stage.

116
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,240
If you're interested,

117
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:23,840
I'll send it to you

118
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:24,600
when it's ready.

119
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:25,960
No need to be so polite.

120
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:26,840
We're all brothers here.

121
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:27,880
I'm only a few years older than you.

122
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:28,480
Come on.

123
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,600
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

124
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,400
Cheers.

125
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:31,760
Mr. Zhao,

126
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:33,680
this is a special bottle
prepared for you.

127
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,560
Today's tab is on the house.

128
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,080
We hope you and your friends
have a great time.

129
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:39,400
Alright.

130
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,360
It's really different.

131
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,480
Come on, Sha.

132
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:44,800
You guys are so biased.

133
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,280
Where's Tong Xia?

134
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,560
Didn't she want to meet him?

135
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,720
Tong Xia?

136
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,160
Don't you remember?

137
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,480
That cool girl...

138
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,240
Hello, hello.

139
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,440
- Good evening, everyone.
- That's her.

140
00:06:58,440 --> 00:07:00,440
- Welcome to Peach Blossom Books.
- Ms. Tong.

141
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,400
I'm Tong Xia.

142
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,240
The first song tonight

143
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:05,080
is one I really love.

144
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:11,000
It's dedicated to someone very special.

145
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,640
It's to thank him

146
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,560
for protecting me.

147
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:17,200
She's talking about you.

148
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,280
She's singing for you, buddy.

149
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,560
Come on, drink.

150
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,880
What? Have you been enchanted?

151
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:53,600
♪Everyone is living
in their lousy world♪

152
00:07:54,120 --> 00:08:00,360
♪Yet we still charge ahead
like a moth to a flame♪

153
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:06,200
♪Trying desperately
to cover up our flaws♪

154
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:08,720
♪Not for deceit♪

155
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:11,760
♪But for passion♪

156
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,320
It's just like your dream, right?

157
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:21,960
Even better.

158
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,320
You weren't in my dreams.

159
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:31,680
I've asked my grandpa

160
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,160
not to care about your background.

161
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,520
My name is Zhao Jiadi,

162
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,840
son of Zhao Xin from Jinhai.

163
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,320
Jiadi.

164
00:08:50,920 --> 00:08:52,360
Come on, keep drinking.

165
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,120
Xiaotiao,

166
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:59,200
why is it called Peach Blossom Books?

167
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:02,240
They say she opened a bookstore before.

168
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:02,760
It closed down,

169
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,000
so she just took the sign and reused it.

170
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:07,560
Come on, Dong.

171
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:10,080
You've been so busy all night.

172
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:11,920
Stop working now.

173
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:16,480
I'm contacting someone you all hate.

174
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:19,160
Then why bother with them?

175
00:09:19,560 --> 00:09:20,760
When brothers get together,

176
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:22,400
you have to have fun.

177
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,160
Right?

178
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,560
I'll take you guys
to have some real fun now.

179
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:26,720
He's here.

180
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:27,520
Let's go.

181
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,000
Where?

182
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,200
Come on, we'll be back soon. Let's go.

183
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:32,720
You guys go ahead. I'll wait here.

184
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:35,520
Let's go and see what's going on.

185
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:12,720
Mr. Zhu.

186
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:13,960
Well...

187
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:16,080
What's with your face?

188
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:17,960
Did you get beaten up?

189
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:20,000
Here's the car.

190
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,080
When are you paying up?

191
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:22,960
Don't be in such a rush.

192
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,840
I heard you already sold
everything you could.

193
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:27,240
Are you still

194
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:30,840
the proud young master
of Pengcheng Club?

195
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,320
I bought this car last year.

196
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,040
Give me 500,000,

197
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,240
and it'll be yours.

198
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,000
I don't even like

199
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,640
the color

200
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:43,600
and the style of your car.

201
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,600
If I buy it, it's just to help you out.

202
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,720
Well, my final offer

203
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:48,800
is 200,000.

204
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,440
Why don't you just rob me?

205
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:51,640
Good question.

206
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:53,360
I'm not the one broke here.

207
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,200
Zhu Hongzhi.

208
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,160
Don't forget what an arrogant punk

209
00:10:58,160 --> 00:11:00,200
you used to be.

210
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,560
I'm talking to you now

211
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:02,960
out of respect.

212
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,200
If you want to buy it, go ahead;

213
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,560
if not, get lost.

214
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:07,600
Dong.

215
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:11,760
Is your dad Zhu Fengping?

216
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,160
You know my dad?

217
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:20,720
Dong.

218
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,000
Xiaotiao.

219
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:22,760
You guys go in first.

220
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:23,640
I'll have a word with him.

221
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:24,720
Jiadi.

222
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,160
Dong.

223
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:30,040
Let's go back to drinking.

224
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:32,280
That guy's already down enough.

225
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:33,960
We don't kick someone
when they're down, right?

226
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:42,080
What do you need the money for?

227
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,360
None of your business.

228
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,640
How do you know my dad?

229
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,000
If you tell me,

230
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:54,920
I'll buy the car.

231
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:55,920
You?

232
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,600
Do you have the money?

233
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,880
I can afford 500,000.

234
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,200
If you need more,

235
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,400
I'll throw in a bit more.

236
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:09,800
I owe people money.

237
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:11,080
If I can't pay it back,

238
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,360
they'll kill me.

239
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:15,920
Does your dad know?

240
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,040
If he finds out,

241
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:20,160
he'll kill me himself.

242
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,720
Get in.

243
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,040
I'll take you home.

244
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:36,960
You wanna sell the car, right?

245
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:38,480
Come and get your money.

246
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:08,880
Close the door.

247
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:11,120
Bao.

248
00:13:13,040 --> 00:13:13,840
Uncle.

249
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,280
Are there any noodles at home?

250
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:18,240
Yeah.

251
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:19,680
Make him a bowl.

252
00:13:22,920 --> 00:13:23,720
Got it.

253
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,320
Uncle, I need to tell you something.

254
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:31,880
Li Zhijin is upstairs.

255
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:28,160
Why did you come out?

256
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,920
I thought
about what you're going through,

257
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,920
and I just couldn't stay there.

258
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:36,760
Why didn't you call me?

259
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:41,480
I was thinking

260
00:14:42,160 --> 00:14:43,440
you might want some time alone,

261
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,960
and it was hard to explain everything
over the phone.

262
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:50,240
Silly girl.

263
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:21,480
If it's not enough, there's more.

264
00:15:22,160 --> 00:15:22,960
Thanks.

265
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,520
You sure can eat.

266
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:28,120
Water.

267
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,080
Oh, you choked.

268
00:15:29,160 --> 00:15:30,280
I'll get you some.

269
00:15:30,280 --> 00:15:31,280
Is cold water okay?

270
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:37,920
You must've been through a lot.

271
00:15:53,640 --> 00:15:54,440
How much do you owe?

272
00:15:59,280 --> 00:16:00,080
Tens

273
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,000
of thousands.

274
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:03,400
Why?

275
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,080
Zhao Jiadi,

276
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:08,640
this has nothing to do with you.

277
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:10,000
You treated me to noodles.

278
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:10,800
I owe you one.

279
00:16:12,760 --> 00:16:13,920
If you buy the car,

280
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:15,480
that's all you can help me with.

281
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:24,880
Dear.

282
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,960
I need to ask you something.

283
00:16:27,640 --> 00:16:28,600
Can I transfer 700,000

284
00:16:28,920 --> 00:16:30,800
from our account?

285
00:16:31,640 --> 00:16:32,440
Approved.

286
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:34,800
Okay.

287
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:36,800
I'll find you some clothes.

288
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:38,000
Take a shower first.

289
00:16:39,280 --> 00:16:41,000
Stay here tonight
and get some real sleep.

290
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:46,200
Here's the water.

291
00:16:48,760 --> 00:16:53,600
[Hangcheng Bank]

292
00:16:59,080 --> 00:17:00,240
Take care on the road.

293
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,480
