448
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:11,760
I'll have her fetch it.

449
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:15,000
Run once I make a move.

450
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:17,360
Find a safe place and call the police.

451
00:25:33,720 --> 00:25:34,960
I'm not Zhu Hongzhi.

452
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:37,280
Give me your contact info.

453
00:25:37,280 --> 00:25:38,360
I'll help you reach him.

454
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,640
