507
00:28:37,400 --> 00:28:39,360
I'll deal with Zhao Jiadi right now.

508
00:28:39,360 --> 00:28:40,160
Wait for me.

509
00:28:40,880 --> 00:28:41,680
Stop.

510
00:28:44,600 --> 00:28:45,800
You don't need

511
